description: One of the fastest USB 3.0 flash drives available, the Lexar JumpDrive P10 USB 3.0 flash drive provides fast file transfer, with up to 24x faster write speeds (up to 245MB/s) than speed-rated USB 2.0 drives. The drive boasts a sleek metal alloy design and comes with a limited lifetime warranty. Now you can quickly transfer 1000 photos in less than 60 seconds and a full-length HD movie in less than 40 seconds.** The drive boasts a sleek, metal alloy design with high-gloss mirror finish top, and comes with a limited lifetime warranty.
title: Lexar JumpDrive P10 64GB USB 3.0 Flash Drive LJDP10-64GCRBNA
